title: Country Girl & CC Rider - Country Mix Gospel Pix
description:
Okay so here&#039;s the story...

My girl and i went to Boston and saw Superdrag play at the Paradise in 2007. While watching the opening acts i found a CD on a table. I figured i needed to keep it and check it out and i&#039;m glad i did. It&#039;s the most ...interesting ...CD i&#039;ve ever listened to. 

Listen and make up your own mind. It&#039;s something you will want to play over and over again and share with all your friends. It&#039;s "unique".

Nothing on it is offensive in any way. 

The CD reads:
---------------------------------------------
Country Mix
Gospel Pix
Chattanooga To Chippawa
Country Girl Sings
CC Rider Plays

"To our fellow Canadians and Americans; 
We are your Country Cousins and
pledge never to get above our raising. 
Speak or Write your mind.

Crossville, TN 38572
or phone

----------------------------------------------
The Tracklisting is screwed up on the artwork, but it&#039;s correct in this collection as it has been labeled on each track. 

I Googled the phone number and it belongs to Hugh  and Norma . I believe this is Country Girl and CC Rider in their true identity.
